summary: This is a fixed version of Lusifer30's file http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27321/?
descriptionHtml:
This is a fixed version of Lusifer30's file http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27321/?

His .esp required the ApachiiSkyHair master file and if you didn't have the mod, it would CTD and you wouldn't be able to use it without said mod, so I just took his file and eliminated that requirement of that mod.

Requirements:
Dawnguard
Hearthfire
Dragonborn

Remember that this mod has to be at the end of your load order (as specified by the author).

All credit goes to Lusifer30 for the original file.
author: Lusifer30
